turn left  左轉 
traffic light  紅綠燈 
landmark  地標 
next to  在…旁邊 
how long  多久 
on foot  步行 
Chapter 5   How to take the Train, Subway, MRT..,etc.第五章  如何搭火車、地鐵及捷運 詢問如何和去某處 1. Do you know how to get to Tao-Yuan Train Station?你知道要如何到桃園火車站嗎?2. You can take the train to get there你可以搭火車到那裡 3. Do you know where to take the train?請問要去那裡搭火車呢？ 4. Just walk north on this street for about three minutes.你往這條街往北走大約三分鐘 5. You should see Taipei Railway Station on the right你可以看到臺北火車站在你的右手邊 6. It takes about 45 minutes to get to Tao-Yuan.大約45分鐘到達桃園.
迷路時的表達用語 1. Do you know where Taipei Railway Station is?你知道要如何到臺北火車站嗎?2. You are in the wrong direction.你的方向錯了 3. I seem to have lost my way.我好像迷路了。 4. Can you show me the way to the station?你能告訴我如何到火車站嗎？ 5. It’s not far.不太遠 6. You can turn right at the next traffic light.你可以在下一個 紅綠燈右轉 
如何購車票的相關用語 1. Where can I buy a train ticket to Tao-Yuan?你知道要如何買票到桃園嗎?2. Right down there at window 14就在那邊的14號窗口 3. May I have a time table?請給我一張時刻表?4. It’s right over there and it’s free of charge.就在那邊而且是免費的.5. One one-way ticket to Tao-Yuan at 3 PM, Please.我要下午3點的單程票一張 6. Have a nice trip.祝你旅途愉快 
詢問協助到月臺搭火車 1. I’m looking for travel guides.我在找旅遊指南.2. We have many different kinds. 我們有很多種. 3. You’ll find them all in the travel section over there to the left.全部都在那邊左方的旅遊區.4. Which platform should I go to take the train to Tao-Yuan?請問我要到第幾月臺搭火車到桃園嗎？ 5. You should go to platform 2A. 你應該去2A月臺。 

The train there goes to the south of Taiwan. 
那裡的火車是南下臺灣的 
