Chapter 7   At the Department Store第七章  在百貨公司 詢問貨品和廁所位置 1. Where could I find the children’s clothing?我在哪裡可以找到童裝?2. That will be in the children’s department on the ninth floor.童裝部在九樓.3. I’m trying to find the pots and pans.我在找茶壺和平底鍋.4. Those are in the basement in the kitchenware.這些在地下室廚具部.5. Is there any restroom?有廁所可用嗎?6. You’ll find one on every floor near the elevators.在每層樓電梯旁你可以看到.
討論衣服尺寸 1. Good afternoon, may I help you?午安,有什麼幫得上忙的嗎?2. I’m looking for the shirt in my size.我正在找適合我尺寸的襯衫.3. You’re in size 4 or 5, right?你穿4號或5號,對嗎?4. Why don’t you try this on? It’s a petite.你何不試穿這件呢? 它是小號.5. Where is the fitting room?試衣間在哪裡?6. It’s over there to the right.在那兒的右邊.
在收銀台付錢 1. Hello, how are you today?你好,你今天如何?2. Would you like paper or plastic bag?你要用紙裝或塑膠袋?3. I’d like plastic bags, please.我要塑膠袋裝。 4. Your total will be sixty-nine fifty-two.一共是69塊52分。 5. Can I pay by credit card?我可以用信用卡付帳嗎?6. You’ll need to sign here.你需要在這裡簽名。 
詢問商品擺放的位置 1. I’m looking for travel guides.我在找旅遊指南。 2. Do you sell children’s books here?你們這裡有賣童書嗎?3. Our children’s section is upstairs.童書部門在樓上。 4. Can I use my credit card?我可以使用信用卡嗎?5. We take Visa and Master card.我們接受威士卡和萬事達卡。 6. We don’t accept American Express.我們不接受美國運通卡。 
實用字彙 

